import React from "react";
import styles from "./Dialogs.module.css";
import {Col, Row} from "react-bootstrap";


const Dialogs = (props) => {
    return (
            <Row >
                <Col xs='12' className='{styles.dialogs}'>
                    <Row>
                        <Col xs='4' className={styles.dialog-items}>
                            <Row>
                                <Col xs='12' className={styles.dialog}>Dialogs</Col>
                            </Row>
                            <Row>
                                <Col xs='12' className={styles.dialog}>Vanya</Col>
                            </Row>
                            <Row>
                                <Col xs='12' className={styles.dialog}>Katya</Col>
                            </Row>
                            <Row>
                                <Col xs='12' className={styles.dialog}>Maxim</Col>
                            </Row>
                            <Row>
                                <Col xs='12' className={styles.dialog}>Sveta</Col>
                            </Row>
                            <Row>
                                <Col xs='12' className={styles.dialog}>Natasha</Col>
                            </Row>
                        </Col>
                        <Col xs='8' className='messages'>
                            <Row>
                                <Col xs='12' className='message'>Hi</Col>
                                <Col xs='12' className='message'>How are you?</Col>
                                <Col xs='12' className='message'>Im fine. What about you?</Col>
                            </Row>
                        </Col>
                    </Row>
                </Col>
            </Row>
    );
}
export default Dialogs;
